Make sure to have a seperate network configured for both sites (Primary and DR) 
BCP-Cluster-01 -Prism Element >Settings>Network Configuration + Create Network   |  MCP-Cluster-01 -Prism Element >Settings>Network Configuration + Create Network


Step 1:
Prism Central>Administration>Categories>New Category > 
Give a Name, Purpose & Values and Save .


Step2: 
Assign VM to the newly created category (LeapTest)
Dashboard>Compute & Storage>VM>under filters, find the VM >select the VM>Actions>Manage Categories>search for newly created category -LeapTest > Add + >Save


Step3:
Dashboard>Data Protection>Protection Policies>Create Protection Policy
Add Primary location (save) Add Recovery Location


Step3:
Data Protection>Recovery Plans>Recovery Plan

